(39, 'Where to buy the glass partitions?', 'https://api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by/storage/2024/06/13/69ea917e46f017befbeda5f787c95ae23cd0ea33.webp', '{\"1\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>More than ever before the glass partitions have been trending as a solution for the residential and commercial industry, with immense potential to grow in the future.<\\/p><p>The style and type of partition may vary per the clientele and structure.<\\/p><p>Glass partition adds practicality to the space and doesn\\u2019t require to undergo any major building work or restructuring. Such glazing systems let in lots of&nbsp;natural light&nbsp;and&nbsp;serves as a energy saving unit.<\\/p><p>When using glass to separate areas within an office, you retain the feeling of honest and open communication, showing others that you operate a transparent business.&nbsp;Staff, clients and visitors will appreciate your subliminal \\u2018our door is always open\\u2019 message, putting your organization in a positive light from the moment people enter your office space.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"The questions arise on how and where to buy the glass partitions?\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>You can select any glass company to do your project: from the least expensive to the most expensive.<\\/p><p>Your selection might depend on the estimated budget or the expected outcome from the project. In return, the company might fail to meet your expectations. Since, the necessary research wasn\\u2019t fulfilled at first.<\\/p><p>When you select the company to work with, make sure to research about the company and about their fulfilled projects. The quality of the system serves as the warranty of durability of the system and esthetical look of partition. It is important to entrust your project to the experienced and licensed company, who will implement your visualization into reality. Ask for their certificate and license. When you select the company, pay attention to the customers\\u2019 reviews and ask for referrals.<\\/p><p>Often and on clients refer to us with the same issue and we would like to share it with you.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>The implemented project doesn\\u2019t meet expectations.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>You find a company online, glance through the beautiful&nbsp;renders, order the system, technicians come and install it at your place; but the quality or\\/and operation of the system is not what you expected to have.&nbsp;<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Absence of responsibility.\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(64, 77, 99);\\\">Many companies out there work without any licenses, insurances, etc. In case of the issues with the system or hazardous&nbsp;situations the client bears all the responsibilities.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"One-day company.\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Of course, this is one of the expanded cases. Many folks obtain experience working in glass construction and try to work independently. They register a company, and unfortunately few of them succeed. Meanwhile, due to the one-day company concept, the client is left without any warranty.&nbsp;<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Additional expenses.\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>You contact the company&nbsp;and after some time you notice that the system works improperly. When you contact the company representative, they request an additional charge for the tech to come out to the site \\u2013 despite of the type of the issue.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Now you need to make a choice whether to additional expense or cope with an improper working system.&nbsp;<\\/p><p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by\\/storage\\/2024\\/06\\/13\\/09cf18d7567dbeca7d4c25251a6e73db2700edb7.webp\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by\\/storage\\/2024\\/06\\/13\\/69ea917e46f017befbeda5f787c95ae23cd0ea33.webp\\\"><\\/p>\"},\"6\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Unfortunately redoing the project won\\u2019t cost you less, it will require to start the process from the beginning and be quoted accordingly.<\\/p><p>The above shown projects made the clientele to incur a loss due to the lack of research.<\\/p><p>Price includes not only the system but outspoken quality, and continuous&nbsp;service.&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by\\/storage\\/2024\\/06\\/13\\/913019529b93a7a09c8e63b7591f61f5642eb89f.webp\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by\\/storage\\/2024\\/06\\/13\\/49cc7f76742fddb3bf0dfc47acf5747840654f47.webp\\\"><\\/p>\"},\"7\":{\"title\":\"About Crystalia Glass LLC\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>Crystalia Glass<\\/strong><\\/a>&nbsp;was founded in 2015 and began developing and selling innovative glazing systems across US.&nbsp;The company comply with USA regulations.<\\/p><p>The main priority of our company is to provide the best prices without losing quality. We guarantee that you will receive high-quality products and timely installation.<\\/p><p>We are always ready to answer all your questions and help in choosing high-quality systems for residential and commercial premises.<\\/p>\"}}', '2024-06-13 23:19:47', '2024-06-13 23:19:47', '2019-02-20 02:00:00', 0, NULL),
(40, 'How To Install Glass Partition', 'https://api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by/storage/2024/06/13/e6f16e5a3ff0909d40cd6035059545b68b9de211.webp', '{\"1\":{\"title\":\"All about Frameless Partition\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>From modern home to office d\\u00e9cor, glass wall partitions play unique role. It can be built from different types of glass and&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.homedepot.com\\/b\\/Hardware\\/N-5yc1vZc21m\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>hardware<\\/strong><\\/a>, which adds spice of customization to meet your design preferences.<\\/p><h2>What is a glass partition wall?<\\/h2><p>Interior or exterior wall structure made out of glass, with framing or frameless. Such structure helps to have non load bearing wall, which serves as a divider of space. The glass partition trending as a modern concept in residential and commercial spaces.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"2\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<h3>Advantages of glass partition:<\\/h3><ul><li>Partition divides the area, without limiting feel of the space;<\\/li><li>Access of natural light;<\\/li><li>Transparency in the corporate set up;<\\/li><li>Frosted glass adds the level of privacy;<\\/li><li>Adjustable to any design and style;<\\/li><li>Glass resists the stain \\u2013 smooth surface helps to maintain clean squeaky partition.<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><\\/p><h3>Types of the glass panels:<\\/h3><p><br><\\/p><p>The panels range from minimal privacy to extensive wall structure. The design scheme and the type of panel is adjustable per person.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><ol><li>Clear<\\/li><li>Ultra-clear (low iron)<\\/li><li>Tempered<\\/li><li>Patterned<\\/li><li>Frosted<\\/li><li>Tinted<\\/li><li>Laminated<\\/li><\\/ol><p><br><\\/p><p>The design features of all-glass partitions make it possible to use swing, sliding and pendulum frameless glass doors with a modern design. Such solutions can use high-quality imported fittings.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>In the designs of all-glass frameless partitions, profiles are used, through which glass is fixed to the ceiling, flooring and walls. Since they are practically invisible, the effect of creating all the planes of the partition from glass only is created.<\\/p>\"},\"3\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Frameless partitions have a larger glazing area and a lighter appearance than frame solutions. Due to the absence of a vertical frame, installation is greatly simplified, the possible overview is increased, and the effect of spatial expansion is created.<\\/p><p>Such glass frameless partitions are distinguished by a small thickness, which significantly distinguishes them from drywall and brick options. As a result, the installation of frameless structures will not affect the size of the room.<\\/p><p>The use of this type of triplex in the design makes it possible to install these partitions in places where there are a large number of people. In such partitions, transparent, tinted, colored or frosted glasses, as well as material decorated with a pattern, can be used.<\\/p><h3>Decoration of&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/glass-partitions\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>frameless glass partitions<\\/strong><\\/a>:<\\/h3><p>In the manufacture of all-glass partitions, their glass can be decorated, namely, sandblasted, silk-screened or tinted. Along with this, such products have a modern design.<\\/p><p>We offer partitions with clamping profiles for glass fastening at the top and bottom. In these designs only tempered glass can be used, the thickness of which is&nbsp;3\\/8&nbsp;\\u2013 \\u00bd . Moreover, such material underwent a special heat treatment \\u2013 hardening. Thus, the internal stresses are evenly distributed in the glass, which significantly increases its mechanical strength. And this leads to an increase in the heat resistance of the glass profile.<\\/p><p>Using glass partitions, you can create a transparent office, retaining all the functions of open spaces (Open Space), significantly reducing noise and increasing privacy.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"4\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p><em>The installation:<\\/em><\\/p><p>The installation of the glass partition varies in many aspects from hardware to chronology.<\\/p><p>But the initial rule is to make sure that the surface doesn\\u2019t have any defects and level.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Let\\u2019s review how&nbsp;<em>frameless walls<\\/em>&nbsp;are being installed:<\\/p><h3>Install tracks: top and bottom<\\/h3><p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by\\/storage\\/2024\\/06\\/13\\/452f9d622652fb4b2bd6145ca986522cf29b8311.webp\\\"><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><ul><li>Put setting block, if needed<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by\\/storage\\/2024\\/06\\/13\\/c68d86d72c9be789dceb8854bf9ac7d06e8b32f7.webp\\\"><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><ul><li>Slide in the glass: the top first and then bottom<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><ul><li>Clip copolymer strip between the glass panels<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by\\/storage\\/2024\\/06\\/13\\/a32f79b208d20795761e7a2344e45acae80947e3.webp\\\"><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><ul><li>Roll in rubber gaskets to secure the glass<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><\\/p><p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by\\/storage\\/2024\\/06\\/13\\/237b18551b2ceb5127ffef227eb2e709cae4b88c.webp\\\"><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>To note, the door should prefabricate for the hardware to be used.<\\/p><p>Having professional company with quality work will help your zoning dream come true.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"}}', '2024-06-13 23:25:24', '2024-06-13 23:25:24', '2004-02-20 05:00:00', 0, NULL),
(41, 'Unfold The Advantages Of Folding Glass Doors', 'https://api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by/storage/2024/06/13/3813b6a03cac1b488d43fe58d3bb0010534d9beb.webp', '{\"1\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Experience the most of spectacular views and expose your interiors to the grand outdoors by installing a wall \\u2014 or walls \\u2014 of glass in your plans. Progressive technology makes folding designs more appealing, weather-resistant and energy-efficient than ever.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Folding glass doors are excellent for opening an interior of your home to an outdoor space \\u2014 creating integrity between a living room and backyard, patio or balcony. A folding system allows the panels to neatly fold accordion-style and remain 90 degrees to the opening for a fully open, panoramic view.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Expansive use of glass is one of the key tools designers employ to create a connection between a house and its surroundings.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Enclosing an area with folding glass walls facilitates flexibility in how you use and enjoy the space depending on the season, time of the day, or your state of mind.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>When choosing an accordion door, your choices have no limits as folding panels have numerous configuration options, from sliding all to one side to splitting in the middle and folding to both sides. Crystalia Glass system also allows installation of an independent swing door anywhere within the folding wall. This means that the owner can operate the single door like any other door without having to open all of the panels.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>When choosing&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Folding\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>folding<\\/strong><\\/a>&nbsp;glass doors, it is necessary to look at both looks and durability. After all, you want your investment to offer lasting beauty and preserve the look for many years to come. Colors can be customized, i.e you can choose any color from the RAL palette to match the color of the profiles to the overall style of the interior.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"2\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Outdoor living spaces are a cost-effective and pleasurable way to make your home feel bigger, without a costly room addition. During warm seasons, exterior folding door systems provide the opportunity to bring the outdoors inside and set up an expansive space for entertainment or relaxation.<\\/p><p>Folding systems allow you to easily expand your space to bring the outdoors in, and to make full use of the living space by joining the backyard, patio or balcony. The main advantage of this style is the ability to form a 90-degree angle, enclosing a space with two or three glass walls.<\\/p><h2>Characteristics of the folding glass doors<\\/h2><p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/folding-door-system\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>Folding glass doors<\\/strong><\\/a>&nbsp;are a spectacular element of the interior of your home, office or sunroom and have a number of advantages:<\\/p><ol><li>Enhanced comfort and functionality<\\/li><li>Minimum opening space, which allows more efficient use of the living area<\\/li><li>Can be installed in environments with high humidity, as aluminum and glass are moisture-resistant materials<\\/li><li>Smooth movement on guide rails<\\/li><li>Quality sliding mechanisms and components, that will serve you for a long time without losing their original excellent properties<\\/li><li>Fast installation process<\\/li><li>High soundproofing properties<\\/li><li>100% insulation<\\/li><li>Easy to use<\\/li><li>Unsurpassed style and elegance<\\/li><\\/ol><p>This bi-folding door system is an integral element of the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.architecturaldigest.com\\/gallery\\/modern-design-inspiration\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>modern interior<\\/strong><\\/a>, which can be installed:<\\/p><ol><li>in offices for the optimal distribution of work zones;<\\/li><li>in private houses and apartments as a way of dividing rooms into functional areas;<\\/li><li>in showrooms and warehouses;<\\/li><li>in sports centers;<\\/li><li>in sunrooms and terraces;<\\/li><li>in cafes and restaurants.<\\/li><\\/ol><p>Crystalia Glass Company fabricates and installs bi-folding doors in New York Metropolitan Area efficiently and quickly. We offer a free estimate, a full consultation on any issue of interest, assistance in the selection of materials, delivery, and installation.<\\/p><p>\\u25cf in offices for the optimal distribution of work zones;<\\/p><p>\\u25cf in private houses and apartments as a way of dividing rooms into functional areas;<\\/p><p>\\u25cf in showrooms and warehouses;<\\/p><p>\\u25cf in sports centers;<\\/p><p>\\u25cf in sunrooms and terraces;<\\/p><p>\\u25cf in cafes and restaurants.<\\/p><p>Crystalia Glass Company fabricates and installs bi-folding doors in New York Metropolitan Area<\\/p><p>efficiently and quickly. We offer a free estimate, a full consultation on any issue of interest, assistance in<\\/p><p>the selection of materials, delivery, and installation.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"3\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<iframe class=\\\"ql-video\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/_A1oWtELB4I?showinfo=0\\\"><\\/iframe><p><br><\\/p>\"}}', '2024-06-13 23:28:39', '2024-06-13 23:28:39', '2028-01-20 12:00:00', 0, NULL),
(42, 'Ergonomic and Elegant Sliding Glass Doors', 'https://api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by/storage/2024/06/13/9a5f92452e1cc3a757c9d1998eaf091b5cee9fa6.webp', '{\"1\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/sliding-glass-door\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>Sliding glass doors<\\/strong><\\/a>&nbsp;represent a stylish and elegant solution for reviving the entrance openings inside the house. People who keep up with the times and are not terrified of bold experiments choose this practical and sleek design. Modern glass doors look immensely impressive and unusual in any manifestation and offer many options of various styles. Sliding designs are suitable for any interior, adding zest and originality to the living space.<\\/p><p>The stylish interior should be thought out to every detail. Doors made of glass are an ergonomic option, as they do not occupy extra space in contrast to the swing models. A glass door is able to make the space wider and airier optically, and the door itself is very thin \\u2013 up to several millimeters. The glass door can be of any color, starting with transparent glass and ending with darker glass kinds, which are practically opaque.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"2\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<h3>Design<\\/h3><p>Presumably, many remember the bright glass door elements in the form of frescoes and other modest drawings from the entourage of the 90s. Modern technologies have produced a considerable advance from these primitive ideas providing an opportunity to turn a simple door into a work of art. Presently glass doors serve as a new object for design imagination and the embodiment of the most extravagant taste. Perhaps this is the option where you can choose the most daring solution without restrictions of color and pattern. Landscape, animalism, photo printing, and other motifs can be chosen to match any interior, and no other material will produce such a stunning effect as the picture on the glass.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><h3>Combination with other materials<\\/h3><p>The classical understanding of doors with glass forces us to remember wood doors with inserted glass elements of various configurations. The modern industry has stepped much further, so today glass can be presented in combination with plastic or metal, which delivers an incredible effect. The exquisite combination with other materials allows designers to come up with an incredible variety of alternative options.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"3\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<h3>Variations<\\/h3><p>Sometimes merely changing the conventional door for a glass one can add as a special highlight to your interior. The glass versions have no restrictions so you can put an elegant glass door in any doorway. As a material you can choose a single sheet of tempered glass, laminated glass or double-glazed units, the profile is most often made from aluminum. Sliding models look most impressive in the living room or bedroom.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>\\u2022 Interior Doors<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>The most standard option is the interior doors. They are distinguished by the graceful aesthetics of forms, excellent ergonomics, convenience, and harmony. They perfectly zone the space and visually increase the room.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>\\u2022 Bathroom doors<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>The glass door is suitable for almost any room, including bathrooms. The entrance to the bathroom is a special mystery of a house. The modern industry offers a choice of an incredible variety of marine and other thematic design solutions, among which you are certain to choose your own. Classic glass doors separating the shower area from the bathroom are equally worthy of attention and interest.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><h3>Single-leaf or double-leaf door?<\\/h3><p>Single-leaf doors are usually suitable for a modest apartment where the doorway is narrow. The second option is suitable for a vast living space. By the effect of visualization, they make the room even more spacious. Depending on your ideas, you can adjust the doorway to the desired size of the sliding door.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><h3>How to choose<\\/h3><p><br><\\/p><p>As with any purchase, when choosing a door you should consider a few nuances. Tempered glass is characterized by special strength; the laminated pane will be accompanied by a protective film inside the door. Manufacturers additionally offer a combination of options that represent glass doors with protection on both sides. It is critical to choose the right door design in accordance with the doorway.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><h3>Options in the interior<\\/h3><p>If you believe that a simple glass door is banal, then you should definitely consider a few options. Modern sliding doors made of glass offer a broad selection of design developments that embody a variety of models. Our qualified team will assist you to make the right choice which will represent a perfect embodiment of the design you have in mind.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"4\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<iframe class=\\\"ql-video\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/74fvsrOmIt4?showinfo=0\\\"><\\/iframe><p><br><\\/p>\"}}', '2024-06-13 23:31:58', '2024-06-13 23:31:58', '2020-01-20 01:00:00', 0, NULL),
(43, 'Improve Your Living Space with Interior Glass Partitions', 'https://api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by/storage/2024/06/13/2cb3cff0945e1967d6a61b59981e8b7ab6be1fce.webp', '{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Glass as a building material\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Glass structures have recently become a popular element of interior zoning creating extensive opportunities in the design of residential and commercial spaces. Glass partitions allow to radically transform the space with minimal cost and within short time. There is no need to carry out fundamental changes in the room, to demolish the floor, ceiling, walls. Installation of such products is possible even after fine finishing.<\\/p><p>Glass is a favorite material among modern designers, especially when it comes to versatility, airiness and lack of light.<\\/p>\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"Glass partitions and the opportunities they provide\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>The main purpose of&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/glass-partitions\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>glass partitions<\\/strong><\\/a>&nbsp;is the division of space into zones. These light, practical, weightless, durable modern structures of small width came to replace blank walls.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>The use of glass partitions has many advantages:<\\/p><ul><li>Ecological compatibility. To be surrounded by environmentally friendly things and to be closer to nature is the core of modern design. Glass is an eco-friendly and harmless product.<\\/li><li>Ease of installation and use. The products are installed after final finishing; glass partitions are easy to use and demount.<\\/li><li>Glass partitions look great in the interiors of different styles. Glass filling can be completely transparent or opaque, colored, patterned, etc.<\\/li><li>Strength, reliability. We use tempered and laminated glass panes, which are distinguished by their durability and safety.<\\/li><li>Resistance to external influences. Glass is water and airproof; it does not deform or rust.<\\/li><li>Visual correction of the room. Translucent products, even frosted and tinted glass perfectly conducts sunlight into the room, visually expand the boundaries of space, making it airy, spacious, light, and warm.<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><\\/p><p>Glass partitions are the best option for owners of small apartments. They assist in solving problems of unsuccessful room layout with minimal time and labor costs, in dividing the space according to current needs. At the same time, such products look beautiful, stylish, fashionable and modern. If necessary, you can install opaque glass, make it soundproof, thermally insulated, and even add a lock to limit unauthorized access to the new room.<\\/p>\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Design features\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Nowadays the construction market offers a wide range of glass partitions for a variety of purposes.<\\/p><p>The height of such structures can be equal to the height of the room or not exceeding the height of a person. The partition can be wide or narrow, divide the room into two parts, be installed in the corner of the room, and be completely transparent, matte, colored, decorated with a picture and even a photo from the personal archive. In terms of style, design and construction, there are virtually no restrictions.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"The many uses of glass partitions\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>In the living space, you can use interior partitions in all sorts of ways:<\\/p><ol><li>Division of one room into several zones.<\\/li><li>If you want to change the layout of a room, a few glass partitions will be a great alternative to drywall sheets or sheetrock. Such products do not overload the space andreduce your need for additional lighting.<\\/li><li>Wardrobe.<\\/li><li>A separate dressing room in the apartment is the dream of many. It is not always possible to allocate a whole room for these purposes. Using a glass partition, you can equip a comfortable dressing room in the bedroom or living room. Since the glass lets the light in, there will be no feeling of being locked in the closet. Glass partitions are a less permanent and more mobile solution.<\\/li><li>Home office.<\\/li><li>If you want to arrange a study at home, you can separate a part of the living room for this purpose. In this case, you can choose color and finish options for the glass, i.e. transparent and frosted.<\\/li><li>Zoning of dining and living space.<\\/li><li>Fixed glass partitions are often used to separate these two zones. Partition walls create a greater feeling of openness and connectivity.<\\/li><\\/ol><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"5\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<iframe class=\\\"ql-video\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/zaNHJ-_pB1c?showinfo=0\\\"><\\/iframe><p><br><\\/p>\"}}', '2024-06-13 23:36:15', '2024-06-13 23:36:15', '2023-12-18 03:00:00', 0, NULL),
(44, 'A Fresh Look at Medieval Classical Pergola', 'https://api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by/storage/2024/06/13/f65184a099b5e276e1cebabd0be4e70d7be7565b.jpg', '{\"1\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<h2>Pergola is an element of landscape design, which creates a great place for relaxation.<\\/h2><p>Some time ago such a word as \\u201cpergola\\u201d could puzzle most of our clients. However, nowadays these constructions can be found in many backyards, pool areas and commercial spaces. These light canopies not only decorate the outdoor area, but also allow you to arrange a chic place to have a rest and accept guests.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"What is pergola?\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>The word \\u201cpergola\\u201d takes its origin in Latin. Despite the unusual and beautiful sound, when translated from this academic language, it simply means \\u201ccanopy\\u201d, which it actually is, because pergolas have a lightweight design, originally outlined for protection from the sun. The second classical function is to support climbing plants, like grapes and all kinds of bindweeds.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>The first lightweight constructions, protecting from the summer heat, appeared in the middle ages. Over time, the design of pergolas has not changed. Modern minimalist versions consist of a simple frame and a trellised roof. Of course, other much more complex structures can rightly be called decor elements of landscape design.<\\/p><p>The purpose of modern pergolas is also no different from their medieval ancestors. Light canopies protect from sunlight, create shade and add to the expansion of your outdoor space. Some pergolas do not have a solid roof, and therefore do not provide protection from precipitation. However, there are options with a full roof, which will protect not only from the sun, but also from rain.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Types of Pergolas\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Nowadays pergolas stepped out of the framework of the four pillars and uncomplicated ceilings. Often pergolas are designed to resemble a separate finished structure, rather than a secondary annex building.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"There are several basic types of pergolas:\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Wall-attached pergola is a canopy, one edge of which is held by its own supports, and the second is fixed to the wall of the building. Roughly speaking, it is an extension to the house. In contrast to the classic canopy with a blind roof, wall pergola retains its main advantage \\u2013 maximum openness. Thus, it becomes an extension of the interior space of the house, a chic gazebo and a place to relax. Canopies are most often used to protect the car from the sun. These structures do not protect from rain, as they do not have a blind roof. Automatic pergola, which can have aluminium or fabric awnings,&nbsp;is a trend of modernity and is structurally only partly similar to the classic pergolas. The main feature here is the awning, which with the help of electric motors is able to open and close. Such designs are usually supplied with a remote control that helps the owner control the pergola from a decent distance.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Then and now\",\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Modern pergola does not have to be entwined with some plant. Increasingly, this concept means a light canopy that is able to protect from the sun and rain. As a rule, such pergolas are installed close to the wall of the building.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>The installation of an easily removable canopy is an excellent solution for summer cafes, country houses, cottages and many other buildings. Modern production of pergolas offers a wide range of materials and structures, among which it is difficult not to find a suitable one. Automatic pergolas stand out from the usual fixed variations.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>They are awnings made of fabric or aluminum, which are able to fold and unfold under the action of an electric drive. The fabric strip moves along the rails like blinds on the windows. <\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>The roof is controlled from the remote control, which covers the distance of several meters. Many designs support both horizontal and vertical unfolding of the fabric.<\\/p><p>Automatic pergola does not necessarily needs to be installed near the wall of the house. You can mount it anywhere on the site, thus creating a great gazebo. The design and colors of different models allow you to choose a style for any landscape design.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"6\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>The most widespread options for automatic pergolas are wood effect and metal. Wood-effect coloring will give comfort and unique charm to your site. Metal pergolas represent high-tech. They are more suitable for use in urban environments.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>In addition to the style of the material, there are varieties of forms. Pergola can be of a classic silhouette or with a predominance of various shapes: oval, angular, angled, etc. The type of awning can also vary from fabric to aluminum.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>The advantage of automatic pergolas over conventional fixed options lies not only in the possibility of motor-driven folding and unfolding. The installation of such structure is fast, simple and can boast of very low cost.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Using aluminum and stainless steel components, Crystalia Glass Company creates low maintenance product that lasts long and looks gorgeous. Regardless of the type of pergola you are searching for, free standing or attached to an existing structure, our&nbsp;Automatic Bioclimatic&nbsp;or&nbsp;Fabric System&nbsp;is sure to complement any area and add to any architectural style to provide the perfect weather control for you.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"}}', '2024-06-13 23:38:56', '2024-06-13 23:38:56', '2023-12-19 12:00:00', 0, NULL),
