(48, 'Luxurious Loft: Custom Steel & Glass Partitions', 'https://api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by/storage/2024/06/13/4cfc008f811cc2b5a067739f404e1364735ab09b.webp', '{\"1\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/custom-steel-glass-partitions\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235);\\\">Steel partitions<\\/a><span style=\\\"color: rgb(64, 77, 99);\\\">&nbsp;delimit the space for various purposes. The divider can have different designs and sizes. If necessary, the metal surface is painted in different colors, so that it fits seamlessly into the overall concept of the interior. For production, mainly anticorrosive metal is used.<\\/span><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by\\/storage\\/2024\\/06\\/14\\/273d990af82564470a83495f8fe6264ecd762219.webp\\\"><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Glass or other modern materials can infill the partition. With proper installation, steel partitions perform their functions for a long time without losing the original appearance.<\\/p><p>A distinctive feature of such interior design solutions executed in loft style is the ability to create a single composition of any room, regardless of its direct purpose.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>The concept of style can combine both \\u2013 high ceilings and huge windows. The modern high-tech abundance of metal and glass creates a unique, and at the same time, free atmosphere within the space.<\\/p>\"},\"2\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>What are the main advantages of a loft-style partition?<\\/p><ul><li>Excellent light transmittance.<\\/li><li>Fire resistance.<\\/li><li>Long period of operation.<\\/li><li>Easy care.<\\/li><li>Gorgeous appearance.<\\/li><\\/ul><p>Simple lines and eye-catching minimalist details give this partition a timeless attractiveness, which will never go out of style. The natural robustness and durability of steel make it perfect for exterior and interior applications. The sleek appearance of the metal has been increasingly popular in modern office environments. Our custom steel partition allows owners to achieve high-end designs best suited to their individual needs and space.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by\\/storage\\/2024\\/06\\/14\\/2890c0cd3067b6570313cfb5e618c103175dd766.webp\\\"><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Crystalia system is a most exclusive bespoke steel partition, providing internal spaces with a luxury divider between the rooms. The elegant steel frames create a range of internal glass doors and screens all with a modernistic art deco design and appearance, ideal for a high end and luxury finish.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Slender steel framing sections, having traditional industrial style, are combined to create practical room dividers. This internal glazing system is best suited for installation as internal partitioning with a modern industrial or loft style interior design.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"3\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Horizontal and vertical steel mullion bars are integrated into the construction as required for reaching the cross-hatched art deco look. Far from your typical internal glazing solution, Crystalia&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/custom-steel-glass-partitions\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>Glass custom steel partition<\\/strong><\\/a>&nbsp;complies with the highest standards of interior design and is suited for luxury residential and commercial architecture.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Our architectural metal works shop handcrafts each partition and the delicate metal profiles are expertly hand welded for an artisan design solution, perfectly tailored to each individual project.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>For the industrial look, individual glazing bars and horizontal transoms can be custom integrated within the door or screen design to ensure that you get the design that you require.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/sp-ao.shortpixel.ai\\/client\\/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_666,h_452\\/https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/12\\/5-7-luchshih-reshenij-dlja-zonirovanija-odnokomnatnoj-kvartiry.jpg\\\" height=\\\"452\\\" width=\\\"666\\\"><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"4\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<iframe class=\\\"ql-video\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/2ukqUPFaoAE?showinfo=0\\\"><\\/iframe><p><br><\\/p>\"}}', '2024-06-14 00:03:26', '2024-06-14 00:03:26', '2023-12-19 01:00:00', 0, '{\"1\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":null,\"image\":null,\"location\":\"right\"}}'),
(49, 'Glass Railing Ideas: A to Z guide to fancy…', 'https://api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by/storage/2024/06/14/b62bdebf64cc53301311ed73f8d2b47ec356bd6c.jpeg', '{\"1\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>The use of glass in the interior design is a modern trend, which is gaining momentum every year. If earlier glass could be found only on commercial sites, now creative owners of houses and apartments love it too.&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/glassrailing\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>Glass railings<\\/strong><\\/a>&nbsp;and balustrades have earned respect for their durability, safety, and exceptionally attractive appearance.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>There are several types of glass railings differing in installation ways. We have come up with some ideas for each one that will inspire you to create a unique design for your home.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><h3>1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Glass Railing on Shoe Track<\\/h3><p>This railing type is notable for creating absolutely clean look and 100% transparency. The hardware is limited to the rails and the shoe base. The shoe can be embedded into the floor, which creates a feeling of glass \\u201cgrowing\\u201d out of the staircase.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Hey, minimalists, look at this! Crystal clear glass, white walls, and dark wood stairs create a chic design and save you from the dooms of insipidity!<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>While glass stairs can seem extra to most people, glass railing reinforced with a cap rail will stand any blow and bear even the hardest grip.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Oh, wood! Wooden staircase framed with glass railing is a win-win combo for every interior. Here glass panels have a gap between them \\u2013 the trick that adds intricacy and originality.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><h3>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Point-supported glass railing<\\/h3><p>While the previous option seems steady and safe enough, the point-supported railing creates a feeling that you are walking a knife-edge.&nbsp;The points or stand-offs seem so small in comparison to 36 or 42-inch high glass panels, but believe it or not, they do their job.<\\/p><p>Glass railings are spectacular in their flexibility. Here the panels have been custom made to accentuate the steepness of modern edgy staircase.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Do not doubt that glass is strong enough to serve as a railing. First, tempered or laminated glass cannot be broken easily. Second, even if somehow magically you manage to break it, the glass will not cut you. It will fly apart all over the surface in thousands of beads.<\\/p><p>The railing does not need to be railing at all. It can be a wall if you wish. The ideas are limited by your imagination only. Therefore, dream on, dream big, and we will take care of the railing.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><h3>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Glass railing on mini posts<\\/h3><p>This option is the most flexible of all in the terms of installation. All you need to do for a railing on mini posts is to have a staircase! The mini posts can be mounted almost to any surface, be it wood or concrete. The posts come in two height options: 10-inch posts are best for interior railings and 16 inches for exterior options.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Mini posts come in two architectural finishes \\u2013 brushed and polished stainless steel. However, custom color is available to suit your most original ideas.<\\/p><p>Sometimes the material and design of a staircase limit the options for the railing. Then the mini posts come very handily. Such railings still look clean and uncluttered as mini-posts do not look massive as their name implies.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><h3>4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Glass railing on tall posts<\\/h3><p>If you go for a more industrial look, this option is for you. Steel and glass look well together \\u2013 this combo is modern, sleek, and can boast of great durability and soundness.<\\/p><p>In this project, the glass railing system frames a dark wooden staircase. The tall posts act as a perfect fit for the curved staircases as at times this is the only option to fix large bent glass panels.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>However, tall posts look equally good on traditional staircases. Such a glazing system does not create a feeling of heaviness, but on the contrary, accentuates the simple clear lines of the design.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>The glass railings represent all the best features of modern design \\u2013 simplistic, minimalist and diverse.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Regardless of what type of railing you will choose, the specialist of Crystalia Glass Company can install and bring to life any imaginable design and find the best solution for every project.<\\/p>\"}}', '2024-06-14 00:07:29', '2024-06-14 00:07:29', '2023-12-19 02:00:00', 0, NULL),
(50, 'The 5 Key Benefits of Office Glass Partitions', 'https://api.crystaliaglass.stg.voloshin.by/storage/2024/06/14/12e9493d37e25b24983bd42512d967be490523d5.webp', '{\"1\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Office glass partitions have become an established trend in the design and redevelopment of offices. This statement applies not only to large spacious business centers. <\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Very often glass partitions can be found in small offices of private companies. So what are the main advantages of such popular business architecture solution as glass partitioning?<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>First, the main and obvious advantage of glass partitions is their perfect and unsurpassed visual appearance. No other design that performs the same function can provide such a refined look. Glass partitions do not just zone the space and adjust the location of working places, they literally decorate the office space, add light and a sense of transparency.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Second, glass partitions are in great demand due to an ambience they establish. Glass, in contrast to the dense opaque structures of other materials, does not create the impression of closed dismal space. Sunlight easily penetrates to the workplace of every employee. It is much more pleasant and easier to work in the airy and breathing space.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Third, take into account the environmental friendliness of the material from which the<strong style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235);\\\">&nbsp;<\\/strong><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/glass-partitions-for-office\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>office partitions<\\/strong><\\/a>&nbsp;are made. Glass is free of harmful fumes, unpleasant odors and other negative factors. Cleanliness and safety, durability and reliability are some of the main advantages of glass partitions for the office.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"2\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<p>Fourth, one should not underestimate the mobility, compactness and possibility of rearranging the partitions at any time. In addition, these structures provide an opportunity to plan the location of the workplaces of the office staff, as the glass takes any necessary dimensions. If the glass partition in a particular place is unnecessary, it can be removed completely or installed in a new place in case size and dimensions of the glass and the opening allow it.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Fifth, and perhaps the most significant advantage of office glass partitions is their durability and complete safety. Such structures are made only from safe tempered glass, which is very difficult and almost impossible to break accidentally. Of course, glass remains glass, but in order to break tempered glass pane, the most devastating blow should be inflicted.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crystaliaglass.com\\/glass-partitions\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235); background-color: transparent;\\\"><strong>Glass partitions<\\/strong><\\/a><strong style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 145, 235);\\\">&nbsp;<\\/strong>in office enhance efficiency and productivity among the work staff. This helps the employee to work more effectively and thus can improve company\\u2019s performance largely, which ultimately leads to saved time, money and resource and provides the company with the opportunity to take on more business and easily handle all the work.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>With the global increase in competition, it is significant for a company to work productively and be at the top of their game. To attract a new client is becoming extremely difficult. Glass partition provides a pleasing, modern look and feels to the office.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"},\"3\":{\"title\":null,\"subtitle\":null,\"text\":\"<iframe class=\\\"ql-video\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/669z2vkY-k4?showinfo=0\\\"><\\/iframe><p><br><\\/p>\"}}', '2024-06-14 00:10:15', '2024-06-14 00:10:15', '2023-12-19 12:00:00', 0, NULL);
